make a progress in life.

192
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:12,375
Mr. Mo,

193
00:12:13,125 --> 00:12:14,833
since you want to get over Miss Gu,

194
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:16,750
shall we put

195
00:12:16,791 --> 00:12:18,541
our cooperation with CICI

196
00:12:18,875 --> 00:12:20,792
