197
00:12:21,425 --> 00:12:22,541
Yin Sichen

198
00:12:22,541 --> 00:12:24,125
has also talked to us about this.

199
00:12:24,458 --> 00:12:25,166
Why don’t we…?

200
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:26,166
No.

201
00:12:28,333 --> 00:12:31,125
I’m not gonna leave her
just because I got rejected.

202
00:12:31,700 --> 00:12:33,250
I can still be Xixi’s friend.

203
00:12:33,250 --> 00:12:33,875
Besides,

204
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:36,791
I won’t give Yin Sichen
the satisfaction of victory.

205
00:12:37,958 --> 00:12:38,575
Come on.

206
00:12:39,166 --> 00:12:39,708
