210
00:12:50,225 --> 00:12:51,166
Okay, shoot.

211
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:52,958
What do you want for dinner?

212
00:12:56,666 --> 00:12:57,791
Although we try to keep

213
00:12:57,791 --> 00:12:59,125
our relationship a secret at work,

214
00:12:59,125 --> 00:13:00,916
our coworkers have already
found out about us.

215
00:13:00,916 --> 00:13:02,416
And I’ve told you

216
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:05,375
that we need to be professional
when we are in the office.

217
00:13:05,825 --> 00:13:06,625
No problem.

218
00:13:09,425 --> 00:13:10,875
I have one more question.

219
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,534
You’d better be serious.

220
00:13:14,534 --> 00:13:15,500
I am very serious.

221
00:13:19,250 --> 00:13:20,000
Cut it out!

222
00:13:21,350 --> 00:13:22,458
Alright, I’ll go to the meeting now.

223
00:13:22,625 --> 00:13:23,275
Okay.

224
00:13:25,350 --> 00:13:26,416
Clean the lipstick mark.

225
00:13:31,125 --> 00:13:33,125
I feel like I’ve reached
the pinnacle of my life.

226
00:13:33,416 --> 00:13:34,791
I feel so lucky that I have

227
00:13:34,833 --> 00:13:36,625
such a lovely girlfriend to be with me

228
00:13:37,650 --> 00:13:39,791
while I’m at work.

229
00:13:47,275 --> 00:13:49,333
Mom, you saw it?

230
00:13:51,666 --> 00:13:53,625
My dear mother,

231
00:13:53,850 --> 00:13:56,458
wouldn’t it be nicer if you
went have some tea

232
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:57,625
and chat with your friends,

233
00:13:57,666 --> 00:13:58,791
or kept fish at home?

234
00:13:59,250 --> 00:14:01,000
Why do you have to bring me the soup?

235
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:02,884
How can you blame me for that?

236
00:14:03,275 --> 00:14:04,833
If you told me you had a girlfriend,

237
00:14:05,125 --> 00:14:07,625
I wouldn’t have
to guess around like a spy.

238
00:14:08,791 --> 00:14:11,625
Ruona wants to keep
our relationship a secret.

239
00:14:11,875 --> 00:14:14,291
We were just waiting
for the right time to tell you.

240
00:14:15,916 --> 00:14:19,083
This girl is quite cunning.

241
00:14:19,708 --> 00:14:21,000
Mom, let me get this clear,

242
00:14:21,175 --> 00:14:22,875
please don’t pull such trick

243
00:14:22,916 --> 00:14:24,250
as testing her by giving her

244
00:14:24,250 --> 00:14:25,291
some money and asking her to leave

245
00:14:25,333 --> 00:14:26,583
like some plots in TV dramas.

246
00:14:26,625 --> 00:14:27,208
Do not do that.

247
00:14:28,458 --> 00:14:30,458
No true love can

248
00:14:30,541 --> 00:14:32,333
be shaken by money.

249
00:14:32,708 --> 00:14:34,125
Mother…

250
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:54,775
It’s not like that.

251
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:00,041
Sichen.

252
00:15:01,325 --> 00:15:02,208
Xixi.

253
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:05,750
Am I intruding?

254
00:15:14,916 --> 00:15:15,625
What are you doing here?

255
00:15:18,325 --> 00:15:19,750
I’m here to see Xixi.

256
00:15:20,175 --> 00:15:21,375
I’m sorry, Xixi.

257
00:15:21,475 --> 00:15:22,666
You suffered a lot

258
00:15:22,833 --> 00:15:24,375
because of the interview last time.

259
00:15:24,666 --> 00:15:25,666
It was my fault.

260
00:15:26,708 --> 00:15:27,625
I didn’t expect

261
00:15:27,916 --> 00:15:29,500
that it’d hurt you that much.

262
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:31,958
Can you forgive me?

263
00:15:34,541 --> 00:15:35,375
It’s okay.

264
00:15:35,375 --> 00:15:37,583
It’s water under the bridge.

265
00:15:39,350 --> 00:15:40,291
But

266
00:15:40,900 --> 00:15:42,375
I don’t want it to happen again.

267
00:15:43,900 --> 00:15:44,708
Don’t worry.

268
00:15:45,291 --> 00:15:46,541
I will do my best

269
00:15:46,725 --> 00:15:48,291
to minimize the negative impact

270
00:15:48,291 --> 00:15:49,166
of this incident.

271
00:15:53,775 --> 00:15:54,350
Hey.

272
00:15:55,291 --> 00:15:56,166
What are you doing?

273
00:16:00,375 --> 00:16:01,583
Then I’ll leave now.

274
00:16:01,958 --> 00:16:04,583
I’ll let them publish an apology letter
right after I get back.

275
00:16:05,333 --> 00:16:06,208
Thank you, Xixi.

276
00:16:06,500 --> 00:16:07,500
It’s alright.

277
00:16:15,291 --> 00:16:16,875
Why were you staring at me?

278
00:16:24,125 --> 00:16:25,041
Hello? Fei’ang.

279
00:16:28,041 --> 00:16:29,666
Tell them to cancel all my meetings.

280
00:16:29,666 --> 00:16:30,750
I won’t be in the office today.

281
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:32,975
Fei’ang.

282
